                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, T</hi> 206). I took the prisoner—I found on him two shillings, and one penny in copper.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I got that halfpenny in change for a sixpence.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MRS. ALLEN</hi>. I did not change any money for him.</p>
